videos.description: Duke QB Daniel Jones drops a dime to T.J. Rahming in stride for a 62-yard gain, setting up Quentin Harris' 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jones' 62-yard dime sets up wildcat TD for Duke

videos.description: Temple QB Anthony Russo keeps it himself on the play-action fake and runs 15 yards to the house to knot the score at 7.
videos.headline: Temple QB Russo bolts to end zone for TD

videos.description: Duke backup QB Quentin Harris' errant pass is picked off by Delvon Randall, who chugs 52 yards for a Temple touchdown.
videos.headline: Temple takes pick-6 to the house

videos.description: Duke QB Daniel Jones double clutches and lofts a pass downfield that is picked off by Temple's Linwood Crump, the Owls' second of the game.
videos.headline: Jones' ill-advised pass is picked off by Temple

videos.description: Daniel Jones sits in the pocket and rainbows a 34-yard touchdown to a wide-open Chris Taylor to pull Duke within 6.
videos.headline: Jones on the money with TD pass to Taylor

videos.description: Temple QB Anthony Russo scans the end zone and fires a fastball to Brodrick Yancy for an 8-yard touchdown, his first of the season.
videos.headline: Temple's Russo threads needle on TD to Yancy

videos.description: Daniel Jones shows great touch on his second touchdown pass of the game for a 22-yard Duke score to T.J. Rahming.
videos.headline: Jones drops perfect ball to Rahming for TD

videos.description: Duke QB Daniel Jones tallies his third score of the game on a 1-yard touchdown, giving the Blue Devils a 28-27 lead.
videos.headline: Jones plunges in for Duke TD

videos.description: Daniel Jones fires a dart over the middle to T.J. Rahming, who snags the pass and zooms 85 yards untouched for the Duke touchdown.
videos.headline: Rahming is gone on 85-yard TD from Jones

videos.description: Daniel Jones' fourth touchdown pass of the game lands in the hands of freshman Jake Bobo for a 7-yard score, the first of Bobo's career.
videos.headline: Jones slings 4th TD pass to Bobo

videos.description: Duke opens the flood gates on Temple, extending its lead to 56-27 as Daniel Jones' fifth passing touchdown connects with Davis Koppenhaver.
videos.headline: Jones hurls 5th TD pass to balloon Duke's lead
